name: Limited Photographic Print : Curtis Surfing Route 66: 11"x14"
description:
This photograph was taken from the 'It's Better in the Wind' series, and was hand printed in my darkroom using glossy, fiber-based paper.

I printed these in a series of 5, which are signed and numbered on the back of the print.  I know limited series of prints are largely a thing of the past with digital printing, but these are hand crafted prints...call me old-fashioned.

NOTE: please disregard the glare in the photo of the print.

11"x14" Silver-Gelatin Fiber print
Signed and numbered, ready to frame.

Limited printing of 5, only 4 available, then they are done in this size.
